If I was by your side&lt;br /&gt;
I know you&#039;d make it better&lt;br /&gt;
But I am here instead&lt;br /&gt;
And we&#039;re not together&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;And I don&#039;t really have a plan&lt;br /&gt;
And I don&#039;t really know how it goes&lt;br /&gt;
I just wanna hold your hand&lt;br /&gt;
Follow me, follow me home&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I feel you, I feel, I know what you&#039;re made of&lt;br /&gt;
I hold you, I hold you, so dear I can&#039;t let go&lt;br /&gt;
You&#039;re my light, my star, my dream&lt;br /&gt;
I long for you endlessly&lt;br /&gt;
I need you, I need you like air underwater&lt;br /&gt;
I see you, I see you, and your every color&lt;br /&gt;
You&#039;re my light, my star, my dream&lt;br /&gt;
